vulnerabilities.title: Prototype Pollution in bmoor
vulnerabilities.description: The package bmoor before 0.10.1 is vulnerable to Prototype Pollution due to missing sanitization in set function. **Note:** This vulnerability derives from an incomplete fix in [CVE-2020-7736](https://security.snyk.io/vuln/SNYK-JS-BMOOR-598664)

vulnerabilities.title: Prototype Pollution in bmoor
vulnerabilities.description: The package bmoor before 0.8.12 are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution via the set function.
